'''Amanese''' was the language used by the [[Amani/Legends|Amanin]] species in their [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Maridun/Legends|Maridun]].

It did not have a written form. However, Amanins had a tradition of oral history which depended on the [[lorekeeper]] of each of their tribes.

{{Language-stub}}

==Glossary of terms==
*''[[gruntak]]'' &ndash; non-forested land on Maridun
*''[[takital]]'' &ndash; battle for control of planetary territory

